## Import



wedata script can be imported using the id, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import tencentcloud:Wedata/script:Script example 1470575647377821696#/datastudio/project/tf_example.sql#4147824b-7ba2-432b-8a8b-7e747594c926
```
